{"tid":2320731,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"前學生動源召集人鍾翰林 被控去年在立法會示威區侮辱國旗及非法集結罪名成立","createTime":"2020-12-11T04:34:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-11T07:44:52.000Z","uid":240362,"like":10,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"831a491236b1dfa73a9205bbca0c4e836695f8a4","tid":2320731,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T04:34:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12040\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F12040&d=%2B91LnCbTcEAXcT2WrppvqWvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=c061ff38\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12040</a><br />\n<br />\n#東區裁判法院第七庭<br />\n#黃雅茵裁判官 #裁決<br />\n #0513金鐘 #侮辱國旗 #非法集結<br />\n<br />\n鐘𨌺林🛑因另案而已還押一個月<br />\n<br />\n控罪詳情：被告被控於2019年5月14日凌晨，在中環立法會綜合大樓指定示威區內，無合法辯解而公開及故意玷污或侮辱國旗；以及在同日同地點參與非法集結。<br />\n<br />\n案情摘要 (<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/11471\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F11471&d=%2B91LnCbTcEAXcT2WrppvqWvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=3c573aa0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/11471</a>)<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n速報：2項罪名成立"},{"pid":"04d2c3ae34a55bd034b6bf9ccc653af6cfe27bbc","tid":2320731,"uid":11291,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T04:35:31.000Z","msg":"欲加之罪 何患無辭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78f1f17466fdf80d4383be4db6a4455b8b828639","tid":2320731,"uid":263648,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"831a491236b1dfa73a9205bbca0c4e836695f8a4","tid":2320731,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T04:34:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12040\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F