":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T04:36:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/874p0/0x0/100/hd/9ac1b60bf660faef0d6b12b4df895e33/stheadline/inewsmedia/20201210/_2020121014084430760.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.stheadline.com%2Ff%2F874p0%2F0x0%2F100%2Fhd%2F9ac1b60bf660faef0d6b12b4df895e33%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20201210%2F_2020121014084430760.jpg&h=a70f0a9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n幾時拉佢?"},{"pid":"57261ee8e44ed32c52a302911510b3ae9e98831c","tid":2320731,"uid":281054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T04:36:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18463c463669f51077538844ab5c0aea15864a5c","tid":2320731,"uid":66087,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T04:37:03.000Z","msg":"香港GG<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n曾經發夢嘅，唔該盡快走"},{"pid":"cef2f68c3976e03ca6b997f41765da9205f21e58","tid":2320731,"uid":83582,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"68857539cbcd6e5e21f03f49847a0aaea5344bde","tid":2320731,"uid":76804,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T04:36:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/874p0/0x0/100/hd/9ac1b60bf660faef0d6b12b4df895e33/stheadline/inewsmedia/20201210/_2020121014084430760.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.stheadline.com%2Ff%2F874p0%2F0x0%2F100%2Fhd%2F9ac1b60bf660faef0d6b12b4df895e33%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20201210%2F_2020121014084430760.jpg&h=a70f0a9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n幾時拉佢?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T04:37:55.000Z","msg":"呢o的法律從來睇人黎告, 即係人治, 唔係法治"},{"pid":"c12e19b379434a7cb19d0dca055cd737f638c427","tid":2320731,"uid":350350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T04:39:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8920def50ca6f5300cdee2cbad6936c226d67349","tid":2320731,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T04:39:11.000Z","msg":"立法會去年5月審議《逃犯條例》修訂草案，前「學生動源」召集人鍾翰林與保衞香港運動成員在立法會「煲底」發生爭執，鍾事後被指損壞中國國旗，被控侮辱國旗及非法集結罪。裁判官黃雅茵今宣讀裁決，裁定鍾兩罪罪成。<br />\n<br />\n據保衞香港運動發起人傅振中審訊時供稱，當日成員在立法會「煲底」外的廣場集會，保安以鐵馬分隔建制及泛民人士。傅到鐵馬外掛橫額，此時鍾等人走近，向傅及其成員指罵，其間有一名成員跌倒。傅見狀上前扶起，轉身後才意識到國旗被搶，並目睹鍾將國旗扔在地上。<br />\n<br />\n傅在辯方盤問下，承認衝突前有成員曾經嘗試搶奪一名女子的背囊，鍾因而上前質問：「你哋啱啱對個女人做咗乜？」衝突期間，傅轉身扶起失足的成員，故沒有看見國旗被搶走及損毀的經過。<br />\n<br />\n鍾翰林自辯時則指，當時對方陣營曾扯一名女子的背囊，他上前理論，對方卻不斷揮動旗幟。他為防其他人受傷，才會拿走旗幟，當時不知道該旗幟是國旗。<br />\n<br />\n鍾翰林在今年10月於美國駐港澳總領事館附近遭警方國安處人員拘捕，及後被落案起訴，指他涉嫌分裂國家、串謀發佈煽動刊物及洗黑錢，案件提堂後押至明年1月7日再訊，其間鍾不准保釋，故他一直還柙至今。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201211/FOMMO3ABV5GXZNK4MWHOGLKIKE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201211%2FFOMMO3ABV5GXZNK4MWHOGLKIKE%2F&d=%2B91LnCbTcEAXcT2WrppvqWvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=e15afd2a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201211%2FFOMMO3ABV5GXZNK4MWHOGLKIKE%2F&h=5cf9bd5f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201211/FOMMO3ABV5GXZNK4MWHOGLKIKE/</a>"},{"pid":"359a2aa8dd18801ffb7a319abd141e01639831e1","tid":2320731,"uid":84409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T04:41:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40304ec99fefc62d80bd80cb956bf0ea0001c1b2","tid":2320731,"uid":103965,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T04:44:24.000Z","msg":"鐘翰林離庭時呼：「香港人撐住」。"},{"pid":"fccf6935df20df616dc349214cd92c94e7f35fb5","tid":2320731,"uid":268519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T04:45:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d26d0aae95097d6012134893af55ad2b8464bb2